The paper deals with the construction of a specific curve in the plane, which is a topic in computational geometry (cs.CG). The property of the curve that is studied involves the behavior of its parametrizations, which is a topic in dynamical systems (cs.DS). The paper also involves the analysis of the complexity of the curve and its parametrizations, which is a topic in computational complexity (cs.CC). The property of the curve is related to the concept of periodicity, which is a topic in control theory and systems (cs.SY). Finally, the paper involves the use of numerical methods to construct and analyze the curve, which is a topic in numerical analysis (cs.NA).
